N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1272.1 - Acts of commission or omission endangering person or property prohibited

State Regulations

No person in or upon the air terminal shall do or omit to
do any act if the doing or omission thereof endangers unreasonably or is likely
to endanger unreasonably persons or property. Notes
